  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Piolets has a superb location in the very heart of <a data-udi="umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77}" title="Soldeu">Soldeu</a>, which has been newly renovated for the 2024/25 winter season. It's a well established hotel offering a professional and friendly service with excellent leisure facilities, and a bar with a sunny terrace, with lovely piste views. </p>
<h2>Central location</h2>
<p>The Hotel Piolets is located in the centre of Soldeu resort with the restaurants, bars and shops only a short walk away. Not only will you be right in the centre, but the hotel is located at the bottom of the slopes, with the main gondola only a minutes' walk away - so you'll waste no time exploring the expansive Grandvalira ski area. </p>
<h2>Spa facilities included </h2>
<p>During your stay at Hotel Piolets, you'll have access to a range of spa facilities free of charge. Whether you want to relax and soothe your muscles in the jacuzzi or sauna, or you want to keep the energetic flare alive with a swim in the indoor pool or trip to the hotels fitness room, you'll have plenty of opportunities to do whatever suits you. If you feel like splashing some cash and treating yourself to something special, why not book a local massage or beauty treatment with one of the hotel's specialists. </p>
<h2>Warm, alpine rooms </h2>
<p>Hotel Piolets offers spacious and bright bedrooms with cosy interiors. Each room uses stone and wood furniture to create a traditional, mountainous base for you to lounge in on your ski holiday. With their functionality and attractive style, we're sure Hotel Piolets will make you feel right at home. </p>]]></description>
