  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Piolets has a superb location just 50 metres to the main gondola lift and ski hire shop.</p>
<p>The ski school meeting place is located at the top of the gondola.</p>
<p>The resort centre is a short walk away with bars, shops and restaurants all close by. There is also a bus stop just outside the hotel which heads towards Andorra la Vella and Pas de la Casa.</p>]]></locationDescription>
